popular_videos.video_description:
Sing along, learn to count and do math with the Numberblobs - your spherical friends from the wonderful world of Numberblocks! If you're a Numberblobs superfan you're in the right place, because we've got every single Numberblocks appearance of the little fellows in this one fantastic 150 minute compilation.

--- 

Welcome to Numberland!

BAFTA award-winning Numberblocks helps children to see how numbers really work ‚àí and master a new key maths skill with every adventure.

It‚Äôs a story of friends who can always count on each other ‚àí but, most of all, Numberblocks is about having fun with numbers.

Each episode has been carefully crafted with the help of the NCETM (National Centre for Excellence in the Teaching of Mathematics) and brought to life by Blue Zoo Animation Studio.

We work closely with the NCETM to make sure Numberblocks delivers the essential numeracy skills that build good number sense and a solid foundation for a lifetime of maths success.
‚Äç
Get ready for an animated adventure and some number magic that you can count on to help your child learn maths in the most exciting way.
1, 2, 3 ‚àí Let‚Äôs go!

Numberblocks is designed so your child can just press play and have fun while learning essential number skills. 90 episodes take them from number names and counting to a deep understanding of how addition, subtraction, multiplication and division work, via a host of key concepts in between.

You can find your favourite characters and episodes on TV, BBC iPlayer, DVD or the Numberblocks YouTube channels.

popular_videos.video_description:
Welcome to this fantastic 90 minute+ compilation of all your favourite Numberblocks and Alphablocks full episodes and best bits! Whether they're learning to count or need help with their alphabet, this compilation is packed with ABCs and 123s - everything your preschool little one might need to learn and grow!

---

About Numberblocks:

BAFTA award-winning Numberblocks helps children to see how numbers really work ‚àí and master a new key maths skill with every adventure.

It‚Äôs a story of friends who can always count on each other ‚àí but, most of all, Numberblocks is about having fun with numbers.

Each episode has been carefully crafted with the help of the NCETM (National Centre for Excellence in the Teaching of Mathematics) and brought to life by Blue Zoo Animation Studio.

We work closely with the NCETM to make sure Numberblocks delivers the essential numeracy skills that build good number sense and a solid foundation for a lifetime of maths success.
‚Äç
Get ready for an animated adventure and some number magic that you can count on to help your child learn maths in the most exciting way.
1, 2, 3 ‚àí Let‚Äôs go!

Numberblocks is designed so your child can just press play and have fun while learning essential number skills. 90 episodes take them from number names and counting to a deep understanding of how addition, subtraction, multiplication and division work, via a host of key concepts in between.

You can find your favourite characters and episodes on TV, BBC iPlayer, DVD or the Numberblocks YouTube channels.

---

About Alphablocks:

Who better to show you how words work than the letters of the alphabet themselves? Alphablocks is the hit CBeebies TV show that‚Äôs helped millions of children learn to read through adventures, songs and laughter. It‚Äôs a ton of fun with letters and words ‚Äì all built on a firm foundation of key phonics skills.

BAFTA-nominated Alphablocks helps children to learn to read - mastering phonics, blending and reading skills with each new episode! It‚Äôs a story of 26 friends who have fun making word magic.

Every episode has been carefully crafted with the help of literacy experts to ensure a best-practice approach to phonics ‚àí and lovingly brought to life by multi-award-winning Blue Zoo Animation Studio. Get ready for an animated adventure that can take your child all the way from their ABCs to reading with confidence.

Alphablocks is designed so your child can just press play and have fun while learning essential phonics skills. More than 80 episodes take them from learning their alphabet to reading long words like 'alphabet'!

Welcome to this fantastic 90 minute+ compilation of all your favourite Numberblocks and Alphablocks full episodes and best bits! Whether they're learning to count or need help with their alphabet, this compilation is packed with ABCs and 123s - everything your preschool little one might need to learn and grow!

---

About Numberblocks:

BAFTA award-winning Numberblocks helps children to see how numbers really work ‚àí and master a new key maths skill with every adventure.

It‚Äôs a story of friends who can always count on each other ‚àí but, most of all, Numberblocks is about having fun with numbers.

Each episode has been carefully crafted with the help of the NCETM (National Centre for Excellence in the Teaching of Mathematics) and brought to life by Blue Zoo Animation Studio.

We work closely with the NCETM to make sure Numberblocks delivers the essential numeracy skills that build good number sense and a solid foundation for a lifetime of maths success.
‚Äç
Get ready for an animated adventure and some number magic that you can count on to help your child learn maths in the most exciting way.
1, 2, 3 ‚àí Let‚Äôs go!

Numberblocks is designed so your child can just press play and have fun while learning essential number skills. 90 episodes take them from number names and counting to a deep understanding of how addition, subtraction, multiplication and division work, via a host of key concepts in between.

You can find your favourite characters and episodes on TV, BBC iPlayer, DVD or the Numberblocks YouTube channels.

---

About Alphablocks:

Who better to show you how words work than the letters of the alphabet themselves? Alphablocks is the hit CBeebies TV show that‚Äôs helped millions of children learn to read through adventures, songs and laughter. It‚Äôs a ton of fun with letters and words ‚Äì all built on a firm foundation of key phonics skills.

BAFTA-nominated Alphablocks helps children to learn to read - mastering phonics, blending and reading skills with each new episode! It‚Äôs a story of 26 friends who have fun making word magic.

Every episode has been carefully crafted with the help of literacy experts to ensure a best-practice approach to phonics ‚àí and lovingly brought to life by multi-award-winning Blue Zoo Animation Studio. Get ready for an animated adventure that can take your child all the way from their ABCs to reading with confidence.

Alphablocks is designed so your child can just press play and have fun while learning essential phonics skills. More than 80 episodes take them from learning their alphabet to reading long words like 'alphabet'!

It‚Äôs a story of friends who can always count on each other ‚àí but, most of all, Numberblocks is about having fun with numbers.

Each episode has been carefully crafted with the help of the NCETM (National Centre for Excellence in the Teaching of Mathematics) and brought to life by Blue Zoo Animation Studio.

We work closely with the NCETM to make sure Numberblocks delivers the essential numeracy skills that build good number sense and a solid foundation for a lifetime of maths success.
